{"id": 715, "genre": 1001, "title": "你想对安全软件生产商说什么？", "description": "谢谢你如此爱我，前世纠缠一笔勾销，能好好分手了吗？（题图来自：Janne Livonen）", "record_count": 4738, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194528BOWKg4TyuDxtS61a.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-06T11:58:48Z", "options": [{"id": 39680, "content": "没用过……", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258013}, {"id": 39681, "content": "以后小朋友们的应用题会是这样：小明有一台电脑，每小时卸载百度软件五个，安装八个，假设每个软件1G，小明的电脑有500G硬盘，求小明心理阴影的面积…", "image": null, "praise_count": 366, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120276}, {"id": 39682, "content": "卸载的时候不要装无辜求挽留", "image": null, "praise_count": 835, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165392}, {"id": 39683, "content": "不要在用防范病毒为理由装上了弄各种乱七八糟的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 247, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401454}, {"id": 39684, "content": "一不小心就会被流氓~~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 7859}, {"id": 39685, "content": "卸载程序验证码不要出现高数题", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198489}, {"id": 39686, "content": "真正遇到病毒时可以给用户帮助而不是促进我们卸载。", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345679}, {"id": 39687, "content": "你的电脑有漏洞，即将引发世界末日。请安装xxx", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 39688, "content": "日防夜防，家贼难防?", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209295}, {"id": 40200, "content": "好好杀毒 别整东整西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362397}, {"id": 39945, "content": "你带的大天使之剑我都卸载了二十多遍了", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412906}, {"id": 39690, "content": "在杀毒软件面前，病毒都不好意思说自己是病毒", "image": null, "praise_count": 362, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399965}, {"id": 40458, "content": "求别弹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407981}, {"id": 39691, "content": "嗯，你谁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 21033}, {"id": 39692, "content": "感谢国内的安全厂商至今我都只敢用国外的安全软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68844}, {"id": 39693, "content": "没清理时，电脑正常运行，已清理后，电脑迟钝死了。怪我喽～", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223300}, {"id": 40205, "content": "不装就不安全，天天弹，滚犊子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297725}, {"id": 42253, "content": "一不留神，桌面就满了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429443}, {"id": 39694, "content": "咱能不弹窗口吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290403}, {"id": 39695, "content": "百度大礼包、360大礼包……", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283770}, {"id": 39951, "content": "能不能做到纯粹只是安全软件，一大堆鸡肋功能，有意思么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 361563}, {"id": 40463, "content": "下个软件你还拖家带口的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417395}, {"id": 39696, "content": "拖机小能手", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159089}, {"id": 39699, "content": "现在完全不用装安全软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258066}, {"id": 39701, "content": "烦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 30027}, {"id": 39702, "content": "人生苦短 我用Mac", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101646}, {"id": 39706, "content": "从来都让我循环装但又不顶用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358202}, {"id": 41498, "content": "请来几kb的 谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207178}, {"id": 39707, "content": "就这么着吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410815}, {"id": 39963, "content": "装完就卡的一逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389120}, {"id": 39709, "content": "打着防流氓的幌子坐着流氓软件做的事，腾讯奇虎百度首当其冲，最过分的就是腾讯，简直牛皮癣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357754}, {"id": 40989, "content": "还好你们没来Mac……虽然腾讯好像已经来了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419690}, {"id": 39711, "content": "谢谢你的安全软件逼我换了iphone", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283771}, {"id": 39712, "content": "360太流氓", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161034}, {"id": 39714, "content": "一个字，日了狗了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129422}, {"id": 41507, "content": "每次修电脑后都提醒不要装任何杀毒软件，每次装了都出问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425168}, {"id": 39716, "content": "**卫士已为您拦截了来自****的短信：尊敬的用户，截止2016年01月04日00时，您的号码13……", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272909}, {"id": 39718, "content": "只要没有360捆绑，让我干什么都行", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404552}, {"id": 40743, "content": "太漂亮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419520}, {"id": 39720, "content": "360的含义不是全面查杀，而是有360个捆绑", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404552}, {"id": 39722, "content": "我只记得，电脑在专业售后装完正版系统后，开机装了某某杀毒软件后，说我的电脑有几千个漏洞，要求修补，不补就天天提醒，郁闷死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406131}, {"id": 39723, "content": "我一直相信全球份额最大的微软能搞好自身系统的安全性", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 39979, "content": "卸载卫士后速度变快了好多", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349668}, {"id": 39725, "content": "我们对于开机速度打败全国百分之多少的用户并不感兴趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 388364}, {"id": 39727, "content": "我是客户，不许强奸我的电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341986}, {"id": 39729, "content": "不能说并没有什么卵用，起码可以让设备变得卡一点???", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 300241}, {"id": 39730, "content": "你给的爱消受不了啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 386760}, {"id": 39731, "content": "网络流氓的背书都能洗白了做安全软件？！啥都不说了，全在药里！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 40243, "content": "卸载时卸干净点，不要留下自己的垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183870}, {"id": 39734, "content": "我有10个管家，可是电脑还很慢，能告诉我要多少个管家电脑才能快点吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411244}]}